WEBVTT

00:00.083 --> 00:05.700
In the Children's Republic, almost two thousand children
 live together peacefully for a few weeks.

00:06.300 --> 00:12.000
To ensure that there is no chaos, 
 each small tent community elects its tent chairperson.

00:12.250 --> 00:14.250
This can be a boy or a girl.

00:15.083 --> 00:18.250
Anna was elected tent chairwoman of her tent community.

00:18.917 --> 00:23.917
This means that she has to keep order inside 
 and around the tent.
